Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Symbolism=The Divine Imprint in Manifestation
By: Hermes
---
You will be led to the knowledge of the internal things which are
invisible to you, by the external things which you see before you. ...
Even so then, we can represent to ourselves in thought the Author of
all that is, by contemplating and admiring the (visible) things which
He has made, and ever brings into being.
